<h1 style="text-align:left;">
<span style="font-weight: 400;">Kikoff is hiring a </span><br>Remote Data Analyst </h1>
<div class="markdown">About Kikoff: Kikoff is a consumer fintech startup offering credit-building solutions that are affordable, accessible, and educational. Our core product, the Kikoff Credit Account, has helped hundreds of thousands of customers build better credit. Kikoff has been featured by Nerdwallet, Forbes, Buzzfeed and others; and our app has a 4.9 rating amongst thousands of reviews. But Kikoff is more than just a credit builder: we are a long-term financial partner for our customers, and we have an exciting product roadmap of solutions to help our customers reach their financial goals. \n\nSkip the bureaucracy of a big company and work with a seasoned team. We balance best practices from our experience in post-IPO companies with the familiar intuition that comes from pre-IPO zero-to-one work. \n\nAbout the role: Data Analyst\nKikoff's mission is to provide millions of consumers with refreshingly fair, effective, and simple pathways to meet their financial goals. Behind our suite of unique financial products that empower our consumers is a vast amount of data. As a data analyst, youâ€™ll partner closely with product, marketing, and operations leadership to analyze data to distill critical insights that help the team understand more about our customers and our business. You'll sweep away ambiguity by identifying key metrics and highlighting them in dashboards for the team. By helping us understand where we are now, you'll help Kikoff chart a path forward and lead millions of consumers to their financial goals.\n\nWhy Kikoff:\nThis is a consumer fintech startup, and you will be working with serial entrepreneurs who have built strong consumer brands and innovative products. We are backed by some of Silicon Valleyâ€™s top VCs, including GGV capital, Lightspeed Ventures, Female Founders Fund, and others. We value extreme ownership, clear communication, a strong sense of craftsmanship, and the desire to create lasting work and work relationships. Yes, you can build an exciting business AND have real-life real-customer impact.\n\nğŸ’° Competitive pay based on experience\nğŸ¥ Medical, dental, and vision coverage - Kikoff covers the full cost of health insurance for the employee!\nğŸ“ˆ Stock Options\nğŸ Generous unlimited vacation policy to help you recharge\n\nRegular team building events to help you get to know the Kikoff team and soo much more! Our last virtual cooking event had everyone's mouth on fire, but cooled down by home-mixed cocktails.\n \n\n#Salary and compensation\n
No salary data published by company so we estimated salary based on similar jobs related to Mobile, Data Science, Marketing, Engineer, Backend, Front End, Product Designer, Executive and Analyst jobs that are similar:\n\n
$65,000 â€” $120,000/year\n
